Julia Sanderson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julia_Sanderson 0 Julia Sanderson (born Julia Ellen Sackett; August 27, 1887 – January 27, 1975) was a Broadway actress and singer. In 1887, she was born in Springfield, Massachusetts to parents Albert H. Sackett (also a Broadway actor) and Jeanette Elvira Sanderson.She used her mother's maiden name as her stage name. She appeared in the Forepaugh Circus (based in Philadelphia) as a child. She then moved to Broadway, where she appeared in Jerome Kern musicals. She was a hit in England, but returned to the United States. Julia_Sanderson ( born Julia_Ellen_Sackett ; August_27_,_1887 – January_27_,_1975 ) was a_Broadway_actress_and_singer .
